{"id":1723904,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-01T13:54:51.817Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"","id":1723904,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["IT"],"original_language":"it","original_title":"Ducati – 100 anni in 100 minuti","overview":"The documentary is a cinematic and sensory journey celebrating the centenary of the iconic Italian motorcycle brand, from its 1926 origins to its modern global dominance. It explores the historic Borgo Panigale factory, treating it as a living organism where passion, precision, and cutting-edge engineering come together.  Through exclusive archival footage and fast-paced storytelling, the narrative traces a century of evolution—from radio components to revolutionary desmodromic engines. It highlights the brand’s racing DNA, celebrating legendary victories in World Superbike and MotoGP alongside world champions like Pecco Bagnaia and Marc Márquez. Enriched by testimonies from visionary engineers, passionate factory workers, and famous enthusiasts like Keanu Reeves, the film captures the unique blend of Italian style, speed, and community that turned a local manufacturer into a global myth.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[{"id":18156,"logo_path":"/3nAuYcaWdpW0ULMvMz6V5HIJmCO.png","name":"Indiana Production","origin_country":"IT"},{"id":14016,"logo_path":"/snclwsIZQbgvqYCBJP8fqNlCA5y.png","name":"MiC","origin_country":"IT"},{"id":141573,"logo_path":null,"name":"Emilia-Romagna Film Commission","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"IT","name":"Italy"}],"release_date":"","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Post Production","tagline":"","title":"Ducati – 100 anni in 100 minuti","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":65571,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":